items.title: Coldest temperatures of the season hit Midwest and Northeast
items.description: A winter storm is bringing a snowy start to the day across the mid-Atlantic, with nearly all of Virginia waking up to accumulating snow.

items.title: Grand jury rejects DOJ's attempt to revive fraud case against Letitia James: Sources
items.description: A grand jury has refused to indict New York AG Letitia James on charges of mortgage fraud, ten days after a judge dismissed a nearly identical case.
